'''Oritvision''' is a [[Venezuela]]n community television channel. It was created in November 2004 and can be seen in the Cedeño Municipality of the [[Bolívar (state)|Bolivar State]] of [[Venezuela]] on [[Ultra high frequency|UHF]] channel 46. Victor Moreno is the legal representative of the foundation that owns this channel.
Oritvision does not have a website.
